metadata.name: A Place Of Power
metadata.description:
A quiet place with no one around but you. You stop for a moment to look around. It's beautiful here. And then you realize that this is your place of power. To some people it may seem ordinary, boring, or even ugly, but not to you.

You come here all the time, take your favorite book and dissolve in the space.

Part of the collection "From Asia With Love".
2022
